When dealing with massive data best to setup a database
Main type of databases include: Rational, In memory, Document, Graph, Time Series
Relational is the most common type of database
Database services provided by AWS, Azure, Google Cloud
MongoDB works well with JS
MongoDB has 3 choices for database deployment: Serverless, Dedicated, Shared(Free)
MongoDB allows you to choose cloud provider such as aws, google cloud, azure,
Price can differ depending on region
MongoCompass a method of connecting to DB's
Can create data API to access data
cURL a method of accessing and fetching data
